---
---

<div class="growth-console mockup-chrome">
  <div class="mockup-header">
    <div class="traffic-lights"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
    <div class="mono muted">ube / publisher / week-03</div>
    <span class="pill pill-warning">Approval needed</span>
  </div>
  <div class="growth-console-body">
    <div class="growth-summary">
      <div>
        <span class="t-caption-uc muted">Learning budget</span>
        <strong>$20/day</strong>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="t-caption-uc muted">Installs this week</span>
        <strong>312</strong>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="t-caption-uc muted">Best creative</span>
        <strong>Finals week</strong>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="campaign-card">
      <div class="campaign-card-head">
        <div>
          <span class="t-caption-uc muted">Recommended next move</span>
          <h3>Make sign up optional for the first session.</h3>
        </div>
        <span class="pill pill-accent">A/B test</span>
      </div>
      <div class="funnel-mini" aria-hidden="true">
        <div style="--w: 100%"><span>Install</span><strong>312</strong></div>
        <div style="--w: 74%"><span>Open</span><strong>232</strong></div>
        <div style="--w: 42%"><span>Onboard</span><strong>131</strong></div>
        <div style="--w: 19%"><span>Sign up</span><strong>59</strong></div>
      </div>
      <p class="t-body-sm body">
        Biggest drop-off is before account creation. Keep the ad spend low,
        test the onboarding change, and do not scale budget yet.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="approval-strip">
      <span class="approval-dot"></span>
      <span>Approve campaign launch on Google Ads + Meta?</span>
      <button type="button">Approve</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .growth-console {
    box-shadow: 0 28px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
  }
  .growth-console .mockup-header {
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .growth-console-body {
    padding: 20px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025), transparent 38%),
      var(--surface-card);
  }
  .growth-summary {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .growth-summary > div,
  .campaign-card,
  .approval-strip {
    background: rgba(14, 14, 17, 0.48);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  }
  .growth-summary > div {
    padding: 13px;
  }
  .growth-summary span,
  .growth-summary strong {
    display: block;
  }
  .growth-summary strong {
    margin-top: 5px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .campaign-card {
    padding: 18px;
  }
  .campaign-card-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .campaign-card h3 {
    margin: 5px 0 0;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.25;
    font-weight: 550;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .campaign-card p {
    margin: 16px 0 0;
  }
  .funnel-mini {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .funnel-mini div {
    width: var(--w);
    min-width: 42%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--r-sm);
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      var(--accent-tint),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035)
    );
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent) 18%, transparent);
    color: var(--body);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .funnel-mini strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .approval-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 14px;
    padding: 12px;
    color: var(--body);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .approval-dot {
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--warning);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(216, 162, 75, 0.12);
  }
  .approval-strip button {
    height: 30px;
    padding: 0 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline-strong);
    border-radius: var(--r-pill);
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--canvas);
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .growth-summary {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .approval-strip {
      grid-template-columns: auto minmax(0, 1fr);
    }
    .approval-strip button {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
